x4freetext: The self-supporting metallic targets of Mn-55,Fe-56,
Ni-58, Co-59, Ni-62, Cu-63 and Zn-62 were used. The
isotopic enrichment of the targets was higher than 99%
in all cases. The targets, which were oriented at 45
degree to the beam, had a thickness of 0.6-1.0 mg/cm2
